posts.title: MAGAthread: President Donald J. Trump Holds a Rally in Uniondale, New York - 7 PM
posts.content:
Shadilay, fellow Patriots! Welcome to another Trump rally night! Tonight, your favorite President is holding another rally in New York: on Long Island in Uniondale. The Nassau Veterans Memorial Coliseum is packed with Trump supporters. More than 16,000 people have filled the arena to the rafters to witness one of the greatest events of our lifetimes: a President Trump Rally!

The whole house is packed! There are no empty sections. Nobody had to be bussed in. It's standing-room only. The only rock star is President Trump! That's who everyone came to see because he's the most entertaining politician in American history. He tells it like it is and doesn't mince words. Only President Trump can make America great again!

Watch the rally with us tonight here on The Donald. President Trump is scheduled to take the stage at 7 PM Trump/Eastern Time. You can watch live using one of these links:

  • Donald Trump - Rumble
  • RSBN - YouTube
  • RSBN - Rumble
  • Newsmax - YouTube
  • Newsmax - Rumble
